1. U frižideru su ostaci jučerašnjeg ručka. (*ostaci*) (There are leftovers from yesterday's lunch in the fridge.)
2. Molim vas da ne ostavljate ostatke hrane na stolu. (*ostatke*) (Please don't leave food remnants on the table.)
3. Moram da kupim mleko i ostale namirnice. (*ostale*) (I need to buy milk and other groceries.)
4. Nikada ne znam šta da radim sa ostatkom testenine. (*ostatkom*) (I never know what to do with the leftover pasta.)
5. Uklonio sam sve ostatke prljavštine sa poda. (*ostatke*) (I removed all traces of dirt from the floor.)
6. Nisam uspeo da pojedem sve što sam naručio, pa sam tražio da mi spakuju ostatke za poneti. (*ostatke*) (I couldn't finish everything I ordered, so I asked for the leftovers to be packed for me to take home.)
7. Treba nam još vremena da obradimo ostatke dokaza. (*ostatke*) (We need more time to process the remaining evidence.)
8. Ostatke starog mosta su iskoristili da naprave novi. (*ostatke*) (They used the remnants of the old bridge to make a new one.)